@DATABASE "Golden Axe"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - G - Golden Axe"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - G
                   ====================================

                                Golden Axe
                                ==========


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Credits = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(46686,255)"}        46686,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Infinite Credits" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPOKE(46652,0)"}        46652,0


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs. Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
